\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Try and test my hand, Mazyd.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Put the knife down.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Tell your men to step away from mine.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Creeping back to the wall, so that he can\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t get got.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Considering words carefully. Up a the sky.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m curious, what do you think is going to happen here?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You\u8217\'92re going to call your men off, send them out in the Junei, and then you and I are going to.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You want to make a deal?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What\u8217\'92s this one life worth to you?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I think you know that if my Minder dies, then so do I. I think you\u8217\'92re assuming that I value my own life more than any other, and so by extension I should value the life of my Minder over even my duty. But have you considered that I don\u8217\'92t care much for my own well being?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Ayram smiles. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You lie as good as any human.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93The veracity of my claims shouldn\u8217\'92t factor into your thinking. You see, this\u8230\'85situation has only two branches\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 you either kill the man or you let him go free. If you kill him, then yes, I will die, but then my men slaughter you. If you let him go free, then you will be taken prisoner, and what happens then, well, it\u8217\'92s . Unless I\u8217\'92ve missed some critical information, you\u8217\'92ve cornered yourself. This does not end well for you.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 I kill your Minder, it kills you too.}
